{"type": "article", "id": 64001, "title": "让家和办公室界限变得模糊的一组家具，舒适也养眼｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-05-23T22:49:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 58750, "name": "Eny Lee Parker"}, {"id": 47567, "name": "Space Copenhagen"}, {"id": 49169, "name": "Maruni"}, {"id": 58751, "name": "Extended Photographic Material"}, {"id": 58752, "name": "Established＆Sons"}, {"id": 23568, "name": "Konstantin Grcic"}, {"id": 26071, "name": "Sebastian Wrong"}, {"id": 17876, "name": "Sebastian Herkner"}, {"id": 58753, "name": "Defne Koz"}, {"id": 28545, "name": "Naoto Fukasawa"}, {"id": 17663, "name": "Ronan and Erwan Bouroullec"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190523204709s327dWc8tE1ukpvr.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #043289; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #043289} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><h3>Four New Furniture Designs by Ronan and Erwan Bouroullec, Konstantin Grcic and Sebastian Wrong for Established＆Sons</h3><p>英国设计品牌 Established＆Sons 推出了四种新的家具设计，在伦敦的 Clerkenwell 设计周首次亮相，设计总监 Sebastian Wrong 将其描述为未来工作场所的“面包和黄油”。</p><p>新系列包括出自法国设计师兄弟组合 Ronan and Erwan Bouroullec 之手的模块化座椅系统，德国设计师 Konstantin Grcic 的两张桌子，以及由 Sebastian Wrong 亲自设计的休息座椅。</p><p>四件作品都是围绕着“家庭和办公室之间的界限变得模糊，人们在工作场所寻求更多舒适，同时也希望在家中创造工作空间的想法而开发的”。</p><p>该系列中最引人注目的产品是 Grid，这是一种基于 L 形或 U 形模块的模块化座椅系统，包括粉末涂层钢框架和落叶松木架子。侧面是金属网格，但可以用木制屏风或织物吸音板替换。</p><p>Konstantin Grcic 的第一件作品是一个非常简单的桌子，带有可拆卸的钢腿和高压层压板。第二个设计 Beam Table 有点不寻常，桌子最显著的特点是它的腿，看起来像建筑结构中使用的钢梁。腿部采用红色或黑色粉末涂层处理，并在圆形脚上凸起，营造出引人注目的细节。</p><p>Sebastian Wrong 的 Lucio Lounge 椅子上有织物覆盖的泡沫体，支撑在管状钢架上。织物上的斜线创造出功能性细节，使织物能够很好地固定在框架上，而不会有任何可见的缝合线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905232049468gTeZPE4imoB3Jbh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735195\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905232049481vIN72aSwglTAfBu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523204949EvFLaeMmsCbDAwIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905232049490zmAtegoPrj1XL7M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905232049501qeYZKCxgjiMyQbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799492\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523204951soLEyCdXcHASKmMD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201905232049527DsiEXURKO4aLCkW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523204952sJa3ghm59yqxkpB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523204953BM6UvFDOCauG9TZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.785533\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://establishedandsons.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Established＆Sons</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Yosemite Mobile Strap by Extended Photographic Material</h3><p>日本品牌 Extended Photographic Material 创作的相机带 Yosemite Mobile Strap，在相机迷群体中人气极高，甚至有人把其当作是 Leica 相机的标配。</p><p>最近，Extended Photographic Material 又把其招牌产品 Yosemite Mobile Strap 移植到了手机上面，将相机带结合耐冲击性的手机壳打造出手机的专属版本配件 Yosemite Mobile Strap。</p><p>Yosemite Mobile Strap 目前仅推出了对应 iPhone 7/8 及 iPhone X/XS的版本，并将会在 5 月 25 日率先于日本 <a href=\"https://www.freaksstore.com/news/2019/05/freaks-store-yosemite-mobile-strap.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">FREAK’S STORE</a> 独家发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205558vJc9yh8NTmCAjLO2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205558kmUiGEs30jprxID4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205559EWVxLCbPdDJSfupM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205559U9GT7q8FWsajnoMX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205558qvNWD5iaQjf6ROLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205600dDBFZ2N5a1XG4cbL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205601QJtOabxiIEgkW49F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Roundish Chair by Naoto Fukasawa for Maruni </h3><p>在今年的米兰家具展期间，日本家具制造商 Maruni 提出了一个新的椅子概念—— Roundish 椅子，操刀设计的是日本设计师深泽直人。</p><p>深泽直人表示：“空间的使用和应用不再严格定义。不同类别的家具之间也没有更多的划分，例如办公室和餐厅椅之间或不同类型的沙发之间。这是因为我们的时代需要高品质的空间和家具，以适应我们的各种生活方式。”</p><p>Roundish 扶手椅的特点是靠背、扶手和座椅都是一个统一的形状，由一块扭曲和弯曲的层压胶合板制成。三维椅子旨在给用户一种舒适的感觉，就好像他们被包裹起来一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205703BuXclvwe720byEtm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205704tGK4FlzBXSbeP2fm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205705kZVJe9AnzjN38Q5B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205705dsISZ4u6N2QKenVF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205703qRzDEKcWtwnJ1hI2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-roundish-chair-blurs-the-line-between-home-and-work/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Silhouette, Ecrin and Opti by Space Copenhagen， Sebastian Herkner and Defne Koz</h3><p>玻璃器皿品牌 Nude  在伦敦设计师 Sarah Izod 的装置中展示了三个新系列 Silhouette, Ecrin 和 Opti，包括餐具和装饰配件。掌舵这三个系列设计的分别是丹麦工作室 Space Copenhagen，德国设计师 Sebastian Herkner 和土耳其工业设计师 Defne Koz 。</p><p>这些新产品在 Sarah Izod 创作的概念装置中展出，名为 The Garden of Shadows，位于米兰的 Paşabahçe 商店。</p><p>Nude 最新系列的灵感来自玻璃的流动性和透明度。以锥形边和实线为特征，Silhouette 系列中的每个物体都有两种尺寸和两种颜色：焦糖色或透明玻璃色。</p><p>Opti 系列研究了玻璃内的不同纹理和反射如何为物品带来流动性。 Ecrin 系列的灵感源自意大利北部的自然景观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205823T5C2S9D6XIW74sG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205824Lg2D6i1Gz8JRoXKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205825pzqR97IFfMWaO5Ke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523205825BTO4YUay1hJdjLbr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/05/22/nude-glassware-installation-sarah-izod/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Lumpy Breakfast Table by Eny Lee Parker</h3><p>出生于圣保罗的纽约设计师 Eny Lee Parker 对手工艺设计一直很有研究，她的作品有一种与当今快节奏的消费文化对抗的以外，粘土是其主要研究的材料，她希望探寻缓慢的传统工艺中仍待挖掘的东西。</p><p>比如这款名为 Lumpy Breakfast 的桌子，结合了粘土和玻璃两种材质，玻璃像是横空飞过去切断了粘土瓶一般，也算是个小小的视觉游戏。她用的是最简单传统的材料，却做出了轻盈又现代的观感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523210021Rdlo9Z7HaiXNDLyU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190523210021QYoy4nvFKiBPkwhT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.428173\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}